text: Olga Drobysheva (born 21 May 1984) is a female road cyclist from Uzbekistan. She became Uzbekistani national road race and time trial champion in 2013 and also in both disciplines in 2014. ==Major results== Sources: ;2013 : National Road Championships ::1st 20px Time Trial ::1st 20px Road Race ;2014 : National Road Championships ::1st 20px Time Trial ::1st 20px Road Race ==References== ==External links== * Category:1984 births Category:Uzbekistani female cyclists Category:Living people Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
